1. *Si* sklona da se uvučeš u tuđe probleme. (You tend to get involved in other people's problems.)
2. Ona *si* je uštedela novac. (She saved money for herself.)
3. *Si* dobro razmisli pre nego što doneseš odluku. (Think carefully before making a decision.)
4. Ona mu je dala svoje brojeve telefona kada su se upoznali, ali on *si* ih nikad nije zapamtio. (She gave him her phone numbers when they met, but he never remembered them.)
5. *Si* zapamti da ne zaboraviš da se javi. (Remember to not forget to call.)